      vibe: "DIY, participatory, unpretentious. Guests help shape the decoration, lineup suggestions and atmosphere. Grows from the same spirit as Berlin's underground open-airs — freedom, creativity, community. The 2026 edition is dedicated to the memory of the late festival booker.",
      sounds: "Electronic music, techno, house, electro, psy, indie, pop, ska, punk and reggae across named floors like Märchenwald, Studio 54, Waldphilharmonie and Schallschleuse. Deliberately genre-fluid.",
      doNotMiss: "The Secret Forest itself at night — the former military airfield with its hangars and shelters creates an atmospheric setting unlike a conventional festival.",
